                        <interp inst="t18380226-825-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 24.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor.</hi> 
